		<li class="comment even depth-2" id="comment-3403">
				<div id="div-comment-3403" class="comment-body">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
		<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/12cf22671b83972de5c006dc6a0e3427?s=32&amp;d=&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />		<cite class="fn">Елена</cite><span class="says">:</span>		</div>

		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://www.gennadij.pavlenko.name/blog/archives/5024#comment-3403">
