		<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/a017d5d2195c041b6a7f95598d3640c8?s=32&amp;d=&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />		<cite class="fn">Yasik</cite><span class="says">:</span>		</div>

