		<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/793f787d4a5630909d582c1bac9ecabd?s=32&amp;d=&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />		<cite class="fn">Дмитрий</cite><span class="says">:</span>		</div>

		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://www.gennadij.pavlenko.name/blog/archives/5024#comment-3467">
