				<div id="div-comment-8519" class="comment-body">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
		<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/94c0662fa8e12ff543cb6652aaef90f1?s=32&amp;d=&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />		<cite class="fn"><a href='http://www.gennadij.pavlenko.name' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Геннадий Павленко</a></cite><span class="says">:</span>		</div>

