		<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/cf7c92de927551aad6b44b9026298630?s=32&amp;d=&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />		<cite class="fn">Наталья</cite><span class="says">:</span>		</div>

